messages.text: Hey, I have a proposal for your Toyota Camry, I would like to rent it for 3 days and pay 150 dollars.
Thank you for your offer! Can you confirm the pickup date?
Sure, I can pick it up on Friday.
Hey, I have a proposal for your Honda Accord, I would like to rent it for 1 week and pay 400 dollars.
That sounds good! Do you need any additional services?
Yes, I would like to add insurance.
Hey, I have a proposal for your Ford Mustang, I would like to rent it for 5 days and pay 300 dollars.
I appreciate your offer! What is your preferred pickup location?
I can pick it up at the airport.
Hey, I have a proposal for your Chevrolet Malibu, I would like to rent it for 2 weeks and pay 800 dollars.
That's a fair offer! Would you like to discuss the mileage limit?
Yes, I would prefer unlimited mileage.
Hey, I have a proposal for your Nissan Altima, I would like to rent it for 4 days and pay 200 dollars.
Thank you for your interest! Can you provide your driver's license?
Of course, I can send it over.
Hey, I have a proposal for your BMW 3 Series, I would like to rent it for 10 days and pay 600 dollars.
Sounds great! Do you have any specific requirements?
I would like a GPS included.
Hey, I have a proposal for your Audi A4, I would like to rent it for 1 month and pay 1200 dollars.
That's a long rental! Are you planning any road trips?
Yes, I plan to travel across the state.
Hey, I have a proposal for your Mercedes-Benz C-Class, I would like to rent it for 2 weeks and pay 700 dollars.
Thank you for your offer! Would you like to add any extra features?
Yes, I would like to include a child seat.
Hey, I have a proposal for your Hyundai Sonata, I would like to rent it for 3 days and pay 180 dollars.
I appreciate your offer! Can you confirm the return time?
I will return it by 5 PM on Sunday.
